
IN HPA WE CAN SET LIMIT MIN AND MAX

IF WE SET IF 50% RECAHED THEN WE SET LIMIT IT WILL CREATE POD // IF WE HAVE 2 THEN IT CONSIDER 2 PODS /50

WE SHOUILD INSTALL METRIC SERVER OR ELSE WE CANNOT IMPLEMENT HPA
METRIC SERVER IS USED FOR CPU AND MEMORY UTLIZATION ENTIRE CLUSTER INFORMATION

IT WILL BE INSTALLED IN KUBE-SYETEM NAMESPACE 
____________________________________________________________________________________________________________

basic hpa file to implement hpa in pod 


---
apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
metadata:
name: myhpa
namespace: dev
spec:
scaleTargetRef: # services like bank/app/bus/or any service for pod
  apiVersion: apps/v1
  kind: Deployment
  name:      # here we should give deployment name
  minReplicas: 1
  maxReplicas: 5
  metrics:
  - type: Resources
    resources:
    name: cpu
    target:
    type: Utilization
    averageUtilization: 50
    
